ers, <a href="https://twitter.com/icy_pete/status/1504992810239344641">according to</a> an Antarctic researcher</p>' class="sc-1mc30lb-0 dIbDxL sc-ntudqq-2 egJWsc"></a></div><div class="content"><div class="sc-1p30kpk-1 dUqyeI capsules"><a href="/climate-change/opinion" class="sc-1p30kpk-0 hYvwLR capsule">Opinion</a></div><h2 class="sc-9tb5ao-0 bXiXts"><a class="title" href="/climate-change/opinion/higher-food-prices-climate-crisis-b2043988.html">‘Shocking’: Antarctica heat is a warning for higher food prices</a></h2></div></div></div><div style="grid-area:story-tall-5" class="sc-1t3uya-0 kFIfFv story-tall-5"><div class="sc-umxyss-1 jflnJI article article-climate article-premium"><div class="sc-ntudqq-0 ifksOd image-wrap"><a href="/independentpremium/news-analysis/boris-johnson-wind-farage-trump-offshore-b2042545.html" aria-label="Read more about Don Quixote wind turbine" class="sc-ntudqq-1 hAUzrd"><img src="https://static.independent.co.uk/2022/03/24/09/Don%20Quixote%20wind%20turbine.jpg?quality=75&width=640&crop=3%3A2%2Csmart&auto=webp" srcSet="https://static.independent.co.uk/2022/03/24/09/Don%20Quixote%20wind%20turbine.jpg?quality=75&width=375&auto=webp 375w, https://static.independent.co.uk/2022/03/24/09/Don%20Quixote%20wind%20turbine.jpg?quality=75&width=640&auto=webp 640w" loading="lazy" alt="<p>Don Quixote and Sancho Panza assess a fearsome enemy </p>" class="sc-1mc30lb-0 dIbDxL sc-ntudqq-2 egJWsc"></a></div><div class="content premium-badging"><div class="sc-1p30kpk-1 dUqyeI capsules"><a href="/independentpremium/news-analysis" class="sc-1p30kpk-0 hYvwLR capsule">News analysis</a></div><h2 class="sc-9tb5ao-0 bXiXts"><a class="title" href="/independentpremium/news-analysis/boris-johnson-wind-farage-trump-offshore-b2042545.html">We’re about to see a boom in wind power at sea and on land</a></h2></div></div></div><div style="grid-area:story-tall-6" class="sc-1t3uya-0 kFIfFv story-tall-6"><div class="sc-umxyss-1 jflnJI article article-climate"><div class="sc-nt