oys-ocean-plastic-sustainable-b2034740.html" aria-label="Read more about iStock-1255120096.jpg" class="sc-ntudqq-1 hAUzrd"><img src="https://static.independent.co.uk/2022/03/13/10/iStock-1255120096.jpg?quality=75&width=640&crop=3%3A2%2Csmart&auto=webp" srcSet="https://static.independent.co.uk/2022/03/13/10/iStock-1255120096.jpg?quality=75&width=375&auto=webp 375w, https://static.independent.co.uk/2022/03/13/10/iStock-1255120096.jpg?quality=75&width=640&auto=webp 640w" loading="lazy" alt="<p>What stood out for us as an immediate environmental crisis was the ocean plastics emergency</p>" class="sc-1mc30lb-0 dIbDxL sc-ntudqq-2 egJWsc"></a></div><div class="content"><div class="sc-1p30kpk-1 dUqyeI capsules"><a href="/climate-change/opinion" class="sc-1p30kpk-0 hYvwLR capsule">Opinion</a></div><h2 class="sc-9tb5ao-0 bXiXts"><a class="title" href="/climate-change/opinion/sex-toys-ocean-plastic-sustainable-b2034740.html">I created the world’s first sex toys made from ocean-bound plastic</a></h2></div></div></div><div class="sc-1t3uya-0 sc-16rjmfl-0 kFIfFv gfWkro"><div class="sc-umxyss-1 jflnJI article article-climate"><div class="sc-ntudqq-0 ifksOd image-wrap"><a href="/climate-change/opinion/climate-change-crisis-cities-london-b2033020.html" aria-label="Read more about GettyImages-1342041273.jpg" class="sc-ntudqq-1 hAUzrd"><img src="https://static.independent.co.uk/2022/03/10/15/GettyImages-1342041273.jpg?quality=75&width=640&crop=3%3A2%2Csmart&auto=webp" srcSet="https://static.independent.co.uk/2022/03/10/15/GettyImages-1342041273.jpg?quality=75&width=375&auto=webp 375w, https://static.independent.co.uk/2022/03/10/15/GettyImages-1342041273.jpg?quality=75&width=640&auto=webp 640w" loading="lazy" alt="<p>“I’ve been determined to make our city a global leader on climate action” </p>" class="sc-1mc30lb-0 dIbDxL sc-ntudqq-2 egJWsc"></a></div><div class="content"><div class="sc-1p30kpk-1 dUqyeI capsules"><a href="/climate-change/opinion" class="sc-1p30kpk-0 hYvwLR capsule">Opi